Package: stopwatch
Title: High Precision Timings Using Mocking
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Simon", "Couch", , "simonpatrickcouch@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5676-5107"))
Description: Introduces ticker objects, which temporarily mock an inputted 
  function with a wrapper of the function that records the elapsed time of 
  the call to the inputted function and stores it for later exploration.
